THE DOG Island is a large island in the middle of the ocean. It is the place this game is named after. The island is in the shape of a dog sniffing along the ground, carrying some large bags on its back. Most of the areas in the game are on this island, and there is also a legend that a magical flower, called the Legendary Flower, can be found on this island. This flower has the power to cure any kind of illness, so you must look for it here.
